parameters:
Elder Councilor Pilia: I will remember that we were indebted
to the Adventurer's Guild.

Elder Council Member Pilia: Emoni-kun, I cannot approve of
your proposal.

Royal Court Official Emoni: Queen Caron-sama is concerned
about the current situation. She fears that the empire will
be divided and lead to a civil war...

Elder Council Member Pilia: I am here to prevent that! It is
to ensure that the Fotizona Empire does not weaken under any
circumstances!
Prince Rex: 'Long time no see, Uncle.'

Elder Council Member Pilia: So, it has finally come... I
thought it was only a matter of time after hearing about the
campus.

Royal Court Official Emoni: I am the one who has formally
requested an audience with Lady Pilia!

Royal Court Official Emoni: There seem to be adventurers
from the armed Adventurer's Guild... Can we consider this as
a rebellion against Queen Caron-sama?

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ohoho, if I were to give a
command, the guards would rush in to capture the rebels--

Prince Rex: Please cooperate with me to overthrow Queen
Caron, and I, the first prince, will take the throne.

Prince Rex: That is the true and rightful way, as desired by
my father Agnos and my mother Leucos.

Elder Council Member Pilia: I understand your thoughts, but
I cannot comprehend what caused this change of heart...

Elder Council Member Pilia: I do not necessarily support
Caron's methods, but it is a fact that she has already
established a stable regime.

Elder Council Member Pilia: What will happen if the empire
falls into a civil war? Even if it has weakened, there is no
way that the neighboring country Tarasa will overlook this
opportunity!

Elder Council Member Pilia: I cannot support you, and at the
same time, I do not actively support Queen Caron.

Prince Rex: You are mistaken. I did not come here to plead,
but to give orders as the rightful prince.

Prince Rex: You are the guardian of Queen Caron's regime,
ensuring that her regime does not collapse by maintaining a
meaningless balance.

Elder Council Member Pilia: Y-You, what on earth... It's as
if you have the eyes of King Agnos...!

Prince Rex: The false balance must be broken, destroying the
foolish equilibrium, and the rightful one should sit on the
throne.

Elder Council Member Pilia: Do you remember, Rex? I remember
how you used to love picture books and I would often read
them to you.

Elder Council Member Pilia: You used to love gentle stories
with animals... You were such a kind child.

Elder Council Member Pilia: ...I understand that you are
saying the right thing, but I cannot bend my own beliefs.

Elder Council Member Pilia: Understand, Rex. We absolutely
cannot allow a civil war to happen in this situation--

Elder Council Member Pilia: R-Rex... If this balance were to
crumble... the empire... would collapse...

Elder Council Member Pilia: Ah... Sol... the empire... to
Fotizona... eternal glory...

Prince Rex: The meaningless balance should be broken, and
anyone who obstructs the path to the throne must be
eliminated.

Prince Rex: Even if these hands become dirty, even if these
hands become covered in blood, I have a place that I must
conquer.

Palace Official Emoni: S-Someone, h-help! Lady Pilia, Lady
Pilia, someone!

Prince Rex: Tell Caron that the balance has been broken. I
will definitely drag you down.

Captain of Pilia's Guard: What is happening!? This is Pilia-
sama, you scoundrels!

Captain of Pilia's Guard: We will never forgive you for
restraining our master...!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
General Atu: Piria... So this is as far as you've come.

Imperial Soldier: According to the palace officials, Prince
Rex has assassinated Lady Piria.

Imperial Soldier: The information is conflicting, so it's
unclear how much of it is true...

General Atu (stabbing without any hesitation towards his own
uncle)

General Atu (That young man may be a monster surpassing his
father, who was called an Ogre, more than I thought...)
General Atu: So he's harboring a dragon, huh?
Imperial Soldier: General, are you alright?

General Atu: The battlefield may have been different... but
in the aspect of absolutely avoiding civil war, Piria was a
comrade in arms.

General Atu: The precarious balance surrounding the royal
palace has crumbled. It seems that I also need to clarify my
position soon.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

General Atu: There are only familiar faces here. I never
expected Rex himself to come, what a surprise.

Prince Rex: Those who do not stand on the front lines, like
you, will not be followed by subordinates.

General Atu: That's a good mindset, though it feels more
like the thinking of a general rather than a king.

Prince Rex: I am merely following the legitimate traditions
of the empire, just like the founder of the empire.

General Atu: No matter how long you argue, you won't
improve. Well then, let's start with the specifics soon.

General Atu: You bastard! Are those the words of a man
trying to become king!?

Prince Rex: To overturn the overwhelming difference in
military strength, there is no choice but for you to come to
my battlefield.

Prince Rex: I will say it one more time, we will settle
everything at the Fotizona Palace.

Prince Rex: If you don't accept these conditions, we will
switch our target of attack to the entire Mucos region.

General Atu: You should know what that means! The
neighboring country Tarasa will surely join in the invasion
of Mucos.

General Atu: If that happens, the empire will lose its
territory--
Prince Rex: Just give me Mucos temporarily.

Prince Rex: When I become king, the empire that conquers
Mucos and Tarasa will obtain a new source of food and labor,
and will experience a tremendous growth.

Prince Rex: Has the illusion that those who do not want a
civil war share the same thoughts disappeared?
General Atu: I understand... I will accept your proposal.

Palace Official Emoni: General, there's no way we can accept
such a one-sided proposal, right?!

General Atu: Have you forgotten that I have the authority to
negotiate, Caron? And that it is imperative to avoid a civil
war?

General Atu: More importantly...! This man made the decision
to attack the imperial territory without hesitation.

General Atu: I will never recognize you as a general of the
empire, and I will never let you become king.

Guild Leader Agonia: The battlefield will be limited to the
Fotizona Royal Palace, and large-scale battles will not be
conducted in other imperial territories.

Guild Leader Agonia: We will conduct the battle with a clear
declaration of war, and the coordination of specific timing
will be done by General Atu and myself.

Guild Leader Agonia: Is there any discrepancy in
understanding?

Prince Rex: No problem. The next time we meet will be on the
battlefield.

General Atu: Agonia, are you really going to side with
[them]?

Guild Leader Agonia: Yes, the Adventurer's Guild has made
that decision.

Guild Leader Agonia: You are wavering, so you were shaken by
Rex's mere words.

Guild Leader Agonia: I understand that there is some
[reason] behind it. However, please understand that we also
have our own reasons.

General Atu: Am I wavering... an old man who is shaken and
bewildered by a young brat's bluff.

General Atu: Hahaha, how inconvenient it is for the
strongest general of the empire...
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
